AltoCenter is Bitcoin and Altcoin exchange service, based in Republic of Panama. 

AltoCenter provides online, 24/7 trading in Bitcoin and Altcoin against USD, EUR and CNY. 

###Deposits
Deposits via Perfect Money are instant. Deposits via bitcoin and crypto-currencies may take up to an hour to appear in your account. Bank transfers take 2-5 working days to arrive to us.

###Withdrawals
Withdrawals to Bitcoin and other coins as well as to Perfect Money are processed automatically or the same day, depending on the amount. Bank transfers are sent within 2 business days. 

